  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q114_NO_PH_O01
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>114. Why did you not avail of PhilHealth benefits? (If PhilHealth was not availed in 113) — Not a PhilHealth member</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Bako Philhealth member</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Dili miyembro sa PhilHealth</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Dili miyembro sa PhilHealth</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Diri miyembro han PhilHealth</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q114_NO_PH_O02
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>114. Why did you not avail of PhilHealth benefits? (If PhilHealth was not availed in 113) — PhilHealth member but not eligible for benefits</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Member kan Philhealth pero bako siya eligibile kan benefits</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Miyembro sa PhilHealth pero dili eligible sa benepisyo</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Miyembro sa PhilHealth pero dili eligible sa mga benepisyo</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Miyembro han PhilHealth pero diri kwalipikado han mga benepisyo</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q114_NO_PH_O03
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>114. Why did you not avail of PhilHealth benefits? (If PhilHealth was not availed in 113) — Probably used PhilHealth but cannot remember amount because benefit was deducted upon discharge from hospital</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>114. Why did you not avail of PhilHealth benefits? (If PhilHealth was not availed in 113) — Probably used PhilHealth but cannot remember amount because benefit was deducted upon discharge from hospital</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Tingali nagamit ang PhilHealth pero dili na mahinumduman ang kantidad kay gi-deduct na ang benepisyo pag-discharge sa ospital</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Tingali nakagamit og PhilHealth pero dili mahinumduman ang kantidad kay gi-deduct na ang benepisyo paggawas sa ospital</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Siguro gingamit an PhilHealth pero diri nahinunumduman an kantidad kay gin-ibanan an benepisyo paggawas ha ospital</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q114_NO_PH_O04
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>114. Why did you not avail of PhilHealth benefits? (If PhilHealth was not availed in 113) — Too many requirements to comply with before can avail</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Dakulon na requirements bago pa man makakuha kaini</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Daghan kaayong requirements nga kinahanglan comply-an sa dili pa maka-avail</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Daghan kaayo og mga requirement nga kinahanglan i-comply una maka-avail</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Damo hinduro nga mga kinahanglanon nga kinahanglan sundon antes mahimo mag-avail</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q114_NO_PH_O05
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>114. Why did you not avail of PhilHealth benefits? (If PhilHealth was not availed in 113) — Limited hospitalization benefits</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Kulang an benefits kan sa hospital na makukuha</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Limitado ang hospitalization benefits</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Limitado ang mga benepisyo sa pagpa-ospital</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Limitado nga mga benepisyo ha pagpa-ospital</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q114_NO_PH_O06
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>114. Why did you not avail of PhilHealth benefits? (If PhilHealth was not availed in 113) — Claims processing too long</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Aluyon maprocess an pagkuha</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Dugay kaayo ang claims processing</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Dugay kaayo ang pag-proseso sa claims</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Maiha hinduro an pagproseso han mga pag-angkon</p>
