  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q118_NBB_UNDERSTAND_O01
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>118. What is your understanding about NBB? — Patient does not pay any hospital bill</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>An pasyente dai na nagbabayad nin maski anong hospital bill</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Ang pasyente dili mobayad og bisan unsang bayronon sa ospital</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Ang pasyente dili na magbayad sa bayronon sa ospital</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>An pasyente waray magbayad hin bisan ano nga baraydan ha ospital</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q118_NBB_UNDERSTAND_O02
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>118. What is your understanding about NBB? — PhilHealth will cover cost of treatment</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>An Philhealth icocover gabos an treatment</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Sakop sa PhilHealth ang gasto sa pagtambal</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Ang PhilHealth ang mobayad sa gasto sa pagtambal</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Mababayaran han PhilHealth an gastos han pagtambal</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q118_NBB_UNDERSTAND_O03
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>118. What is your understanding about NBB? — Medicine and service are already included</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Kabilang na an mga gamot asin serbisyo</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Apil na ang tambal ug serbisyo</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Apil na ang tambal ug serbisyo</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Kaupod na an medisina ngan serbisyo</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q118_NBB_UNDERSTAND_O04
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>118. What is your understanding about NBB? — No cash payment required upon discharge</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Warang cash payment bago pa idischarge</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Walay cash nga bayranon sa pag-discharge</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Dili kinahanglan mobayad ug cash paggawas sa ospital</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Waray kinahanglan nga bayad hin kwarta ha paggawas</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q118_NBB_UNDERSTAND_O05
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>118. What is your understanding about NBB? — Applies only to certain patients or hospitals</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Aplikable sana sa piling mga pasyente o ospital</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Nagamit lamang sa pipila ka pasyente o mga ospital</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Para lang sa pipila ka pasyente o ospital</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Aplikado la ha pipira nga pasyente o ospital</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q118_NBB_UNDERSTAND_O06
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>118. What is your understanding about NBB? — Bills are settled between the hospital and PhilHealth</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Mabayad kaan an ospital asin PhilHealth</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Ang bayronon gi-settle tali sa ospital ug PhilHealth</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Ang bayronon gihusay tali sa ospital ug PhilHealth</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Gin-aareglo an mga baraydan ha butnga han ospital ngan PhilHealth</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q118_NBB_UNDERSTAND_O07
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>118. What is your understanding about NBB? — Patients should not be charged extra fees</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Dai dapat singilon nin dagdag na bayadan an pasyente</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Dili dapat singlan og dugang bayronon ang pasyente</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Ang mga pasyente dili angay pangayoan og dugang bayad</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>An mga pasyente diri angay suktan hin dugang nga bayad</p>
