  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q121_ZBB_UNDERSTAND_O05
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>121. What is your understanding about ZBB? — Applies only to PhilHealth members and DOH-run hospitals</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Pwede sana ini sa mga Philhealth na members asin mga DOH-run hospitals</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Nagamit lamang sa pipila ka pasyente o mga ospital</p>
