            <p>160. If generic, why did you buy generic medicine? — Other (specify) text</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>160. If generic, why did you buy generic medicine? — Other (specify) text</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>160. If generic, why did you buy generic medicine? — Other (specify) text</p>
