  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q161_WHY_BRANDED_O01
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>161. If branded, why did you buy branded medicine? — Branded medicine is more effective than generic</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>An branded na bulong ay mas effective kesa sa generic</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Mas epektibo ang branded nga tambal kaysa generic</p>
          CEB: |
