    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>177. As it was not a referral, why did you decide to visit a hospital? — Facility is usual source of care</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Ini an karaniwang pinupuntahan kong pasilidad</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Kasagarang gigikanan sa pag-atiman sa panglawas ang pasilidad</p>
          CEB: |
