  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q177_WHY_HOSPITAL_O04
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>177. As it was not a referral, why did you decide to visit a hospital? — Facility is the only place that can perform a certain test</p>
          BCL: |
